When user asks to publish a draft:

SOURCE:
drafts/<category>/<filename>.md

TARGET:
docs/<category>/posts/<slug>.html


STEPS:

1. Detect category from folder name:

drafts/mes → docs/mes/posts
drafts/dms → docs/dms/posts
drafts/ba → docs/ba/posts
drafts/linh-tinh → docs/linh-tinh/posts


2. Generate slug from filename:

Rules:

lowercase
remove Vietnamese accents
replace spaces with hyphen
ascii only

Example:

"mes không thất bại vì công nghệ.md"

→ mes-khong-that-bai-vi-cong-nghe.html


3. Convert markdown to HTML:

paragraph → <p>
line break → new paragraph
preserve headings if exist


4. Apply template:

templates/post-template.html

Replace variables:

{{TITLE}}
{{DATE}} = current year
{{CATEGORY}}
{{CONTENT}}


5. Save file:

docs/<category>/posts/<slug>.html


6. Update category index:

docs/<category>/index.html

Insert BEFORE:

</div>

inside:

<div class="posts">


Format:

<div class="post-item">
    <a href="posts/<slug>.html">
        {{TITLE}}
    </a>
</div>

<div class="post-year">
    {{DATE}}
</div>


7. DO NOT modify drafts folder

8. DO NOT modify other categories
